        {
            "title": "油價上漲,歐洲主要股市因假日休市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週一,歐洲主要股市因假日休市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,油價短暫回升至每桶110美元以上,此前總統唐納德·川普升級了對伊朗的威脅,為該國重新開放荷莫茲海峽設定了週二的最後期限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在社交媒體貼文和媒體訪問中發出復活節警告,稱如果荷莫茲海峽這條關鍵水道在週二晚上之前不解除封鎖,美國將打擊伊朗的電力設施。全球約五分之一的石油通過這條海峽運輸。伊朗已拒絕這一最後通牒。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普此前曾要求德黑蘭在週一之前達成協議並向油輪開放該海峽。這條持續數週的封鎖可能對世界各國造成重大壓力,帶來新一輪通脹壓力,可能拖累更廣泛的經濟增長。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4cd05d1d-6a08-3ece-a260-8edd8849b8e7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自2月下旬美國和以色列聯合襲擊伊朗以來,油價大幅飆升,原因是市場擔憂用於各行業的關鍵能源產品供應受限。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球基準布蘭特原油期貨最新上漲0.3%,至每桶109.37美元。在戰爭爆發前,布蘭特合約的交易價格約為每桶70美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管市場仍處於緊張狀態,但出現了一些跡象表明伊朗對荷莫茲海峽的控制可能略有鬆動。路透社援引知情人士報導稱,伊朗和美國已收到結束敵對行動並重新開放海峽的框架方案。報導稱,該計劃最早可能在週一生效。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週六,伊朗還批准伊拉克使用荷莫茲海峽,延續了德黑蘭逐國重新開放這一咽喉要道的趨勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%9B%A0%E5%81%87%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%91%E5%B8%82-082320704.html",
