        {
            "title": "中東風暴致供應鏈斷裂！卡達40餘艘液化天然氣運輸船困守亞洲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uKbqUEDTSRtb1VKuoUmLMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/0de7ade9e311a1ddf740b1a3c774f145\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E8%87%B4%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%8F%88%E6%96%B7%E8%A3%82-%E5%8D%A1%E9%81%9440%E9%A4%98%E8%89%98%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E8%88%B9%E5%9B%B0%E5%AE%88%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2-074002320.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-06 16:23:42",
