        {
            "title": "伊朗戰爭信號相互矛盾 黃金價格下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X1m7Vz3egnfwoO0LW0ibhQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB8N174_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 黃金價格週一在亞洲交易時段下跌,儘管上週錄得漲幅,原因是美國總統唐納德·川普警告稱,如果伊朗未能在週二之前重新開放<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>,中東局勢將進一步升級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間00:04(北京時間12:04),現貨黃金下跌0.7%至每盎司4,644.74美元。黃金期貨下跌0.2%至每盎司4,672.75美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金在上週上漲4%,但在週四最後一個交易日回吐了大部分漲幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場關注焦點仍集中在川普總統向伊朗發出的最新最後通牒,要求其必須在週二美國東部時間晚上8:00之前恢復霍爾木茲海峽的航運,否則將面臨嚴重後果。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-db9a9a62-9f81-3dfa-a1f3-4514568b4cd2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在週末於Truth Social發文時加強了警告力度,稱\"週二將是發電廠日和橋樑日,在伊朗合二為一\",暗示如果這條戰略水道的油輪交通未能恢復,伊朗的民用基礎設施可能成為打擊目標。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,Axios週日晚間的一份報導稱,美國、伊朗和地區調解人正在討論可能實施45天停火的條款,這最終可能導致達成結束戰爭的更廣泛協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">霍爾木茲海峽承載著全球約五分之一的石油運輸量,供應中斷導致油價今年上漲逾一倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價上漲加劇了通脹擔憂,限制了黃金的上漲空間,因為投資者越來越預期美國利率將在更長時間內維持高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者還在評估美國最新的就業數據,該數據在許多市場因耶穌受難日假期休市期間公佈,顯示勞動力市場韌性強於預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數週一在亞洲交易時段上漲0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他貴金屬方面,白銀價格下跌0.6%至每盎司72.58美元,而鉑金下跌0.4%至每盎司1,985.60美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
